@startuml 08_User_Journey
!theme plain

skinparam backgroundColor #F5F7FA
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam Padding 5
skinparam ArrowThickness 1.5

skinparam title {
  FontSize 17
  FontStyle bold
  FontColor #1A237E
  BackgroundColor #E8EAF6
  BorderColor #3F51B5
  BorderThickness 2
}

skinparam activity {
  BackgroundColor #FFFFFF
  BorderColor #78909C
  BorderThickness 1.5
  ArrowColor #455A64
  FontColor #263238
  FontSize 11
  StartColor #2E7D32
  EndColor #C62828
  DiamondBackgroundColor #FFFDE7
  DiamondBorderColor #FFA000
  DiamondFontColor #4E342E
}

skinparam note {
  BackgroundColor #FFF8E1
  BorderColor #FFB300
  FontColor #4E342E
  FontSize 10
  BorderThickness 1.5
}

title <b>3D Data Quality Framework  \u00b7  DQ Rule User Journey</b>\n<size:12>Discover  \u2192  Create  \u2192  Validate  \u2192  Review  \u2192  Approve  \u2192  Deploy  \u2192  Monitor  \u2192  Improve</size>

|#BBDEFB| User |
|#C8E6C9| DQ Chatbot App |
|#FFE082| DQ Backend App |
|#F8BBD0| Approval Gateway |
|#D1C4E9| Platform (Automated) |

legend top left
  <b><size:12>Rule Lifecycle States</size></b>
  <font color="#F57F17"><b>PROPOSED</b></font> \u2192 <font color="#1565C0"><b>PENDING_APPROVAL</b></font> \u2192 <font color="#2E7D32"><b>APPROVED</b></font> \u2192 <font color="#1B5E20"><b>ACTIVE</b></font>
                               \u2514\u2192 <font color="#B71C1C"><b>REJECTED</b></font>  (revise & resubmit)
  <font color="#1B5E20"><b>ACTIVE</b></font> \u2194 <font color="#616161"><b>INACTIVE / DISABLED</b></font>   (pause or kill-switch)
  <font color="#1B5E20"><b>ACTIVE</b></font> \u2192 <font color="#757575"><b>DEPRECATED</b></font> \u2192 <font color="#424242"><b>ARCHIVED</b></font>
endlegend

start

'
' -------------------------------------
'  PHASE 1 . DISCOVER
' -------------------------------------
|User|
#1565C0:<color:#FFFFFF><b>  \u2460 DISCOVER  \u00b7  Explore & Ask Questions  </b></color>;

:Open **DQ Chatbot App**\n//DQ Assistant chat in Databricks//;
note right #BBDEFB: Authenticated via Databricks SSO\nWorkspace identity auto-applied

|DQ Chatbot App|
:Greet user -- present options:\n  \u2022 Ask Q&A about data quality\n  \u2022 Propose a new DQ rule\n  \u2022 Browse rules + coverage gaps\n  \u2022 Check execution results / trends\n  \u2022 Manage exceptions;

repeat
  |User|
  :Ask a natural language question:\n  //"DRRI score for gold.customer?"//\n  //"Which jobs failed last night?"//\n  //"Anomalies for adiClub orders this week"//\n  //"Top 5 noisiest rules by false positives"//;

  |DQ Chatbot App|
  :Classify intent = **READ**\nGenerate **SELECT** SQL -- read-only via Unity Catalog;
  note right #C8E6C9
    Queries live Delta tables:
    \u2022 anomaly_check_config
    \u2022 check_execution_log
    \u2022 DIGITAL_DATA_ANOMALIES
    \u2022 table_daily_metrics
  end note

  :Return structured answer:\n  //"DRRI: 72/100 -- 3 failing checks + freshness drift"//\n  //"Run #4821 FAILED -- timeout on fact_sales"//;

  |User|
  :Read answer \u00b7 drill down\n//filter by market, brand, date, column//;
repeat while (More questions?) is (Yes) not (No -- done)

|DQ Chatbot App|
:Summarise coverage gaps\nand recommended next checks;
note right #C8E6C9: Any answer can pivot directly\ninto **CREATE** to close a gap

'
' -------------------------------------
'  PHASE 2 . CREATE
' -------------------------------------
|User|
#2E7D32:<color:#FFFFFF><b>  \u2461 CREATE  \u00b7  Propose a New DQ Rule  </b></color>;

:Type rule request in natural language\n//"Create a null check for customer_email in gold.customer"//;

|DQ Chatbot App|
:Classify intent = **WRITE**\nInvoke DQ Backend App via UC tool;

|DQ Backend App|
:Map request to known DQ check catalog;

if (Check type supported?) then (No -- new type)
  :Inform user -- collect details:\n  1) Business intent\n  2) Pass / fail condition\n  3) Target table + columns\n  4) Threshold\n  5) Sample expectation;

  |User|
  :Describe rule intent\n//(or provide SQL if known)//;

  |DQ Backend App|
  :Propose best-fit approach:\n  **A)** Map to nearest existing check\n  **B)** Generate custom DQ SQL\n  **C)** Submit as new check-type request;

  |User|
  :Review proposal \u2192 choose A / B / C;

  if (A or B -- proceed?) then (Yes)
    |DQ Backend App|
    :Generate rule definition\nand expected behaviour;
  else (C -- new type)
    |Approval Gateway|
    :Raise **New DQ Type** review\nData Governance + Tech Lead;
    |User|
    :Track request status\u00b7 await decision;
    stop
  endif

else (Yes -- supported type)
  |DQ Backend App|
  :Generate rule draft for check type;
endif

'
' -------------------------------------
'  PHASE 3 . VALIDATE
' -------------------------------------
|DQ Backend App|
#E65100:<color:#FFFFFF><b>  \u2462 VALIDATE  \u00b7  Automated Quality Gates  </b></color>;

:\u26D4 **Security Guard**\n//SELECT-only \u00b7 block injection / DDL / DML//;
:\u2714 **SQL Validator**\n//Syntax \u00b7 Schema \u00b7 Cost estimate \u00b7 Partition alignment//;
:\u26A0 **Duplicate Detector**\n//Similarity vs active rules in anomaly_check_config//;

|DQ Chatbot App|
:Present validation results;

|User|
:Review rule definition + SQL preview;

if (Edits needed?) then (Yes)
  :Request edits or add constraints;
  |DQ Backend App|
  :Re-validate \u2192 return revised rule;
  |User|
else (No -- looks good)
endif

if (Duplicate found?) then (Yes)
  |DQ Chatbot App|
  :Show similar rule(s) with similarity %;
  |User|
  :Choose: reuse \u00b7 modify \u00b7 proceed anyway;
  if (Cancelled?) then (Yes)
    stop
  endif
else (No duplicate)
endif

|User|
:Provide metadata:\n  Owner \u00b7 Frequency \u00b7 Priority (P1/P2/P3)\n  Thresholds \u00b7 Description \u00b7 Notifications;

|DQ Backend App|
:Calculate **Trend Score**\nfrom 30-day execution history for table/column;
note right #FFF3E0: No history? \u2192 "Insufficient data"\nRule creation still permitted

|DQ Chatbot App|
:Display **Trend Score**:\n  PASS: {pass_pct}%  /  FAIL: {fail_pct}%\n  Confidence: {High / Medium / Low};
note right #C8E6C9: Approver sees the same score\non the Approval Dashboard

|User|
:Review trend + impact \u2192 Confirm submission;

|DQ Backend App|
:INSERT \u2192 anomaly_check_config\nAudit LOG: CREATE \u2192 rule_audit_log;
note right #FFF8E1: <font color="#F57F17"><b>STATUS = PROPOSED (DRAFT)</b></font>\nis_active = false

'
' -------------------------------------
'  PHASE 4-5 . REVIEW + APPROVE
' -------------------------------------
|Approval Gateway|
#6A1B9A:<color:#FFFFFF><b>  \u2463\u2464 REVIEW + APPROVE  \u00b7  Governance Gate  </b></color>;

:Is submitter == table owner?;

if (Self-approval?) then (Yes -- owner)
  :Auto-approve\nSET is_active = true, auto_approved = true;
  note right #C8E6C9: <font color="#1B5E20"><b>STATUS = APPROVED \u2192 ACTIVE</b></font>
  |User|
  :Rule **ACTIVE** immediately\nRule ID: {config_id}\nNext run: {next_scheduled_run};
else (No -- peer review needed)
  :Set status = PENDING_APPROVAL;
  note right #FFF3E0: <font color="#1565C0"><b>STATUS = PENDING_APPROVAL</b></font>\nis_active = false (awaiting review)
  :Notify PO + Tech Lead\nEmail + Jira ticket \u00b7 48 h SLA;

  |User|
  :Submitted -- monitor status in DQ Chatbot App;

  |Approval Gateway|
  :PO / Tech Lead reviews:\n  rule definition \u00b7 trend score \u00b7 blast radius;

  if (Approved?) then (Yes)
    :SET is_active = true\nLOG APPROVED in audit trail;
    note right #C8E6C9: <font color="#1B5E20"><b>STATUS = APPROVED \u2192 ACTIVE</b></font>
    |User|
    :Rule **ACTIVE** -- email confirmed\nRule ID: {config_id};
  else (Rejected)
    :SET status = REJECTED\nCapture rejection reason;
    note right #FFCDD2: <font color="#B71C1C"><b>STATUS = REJECTED</b></font>\nis_active = false
    |User|
    :Rule rejected \u00b7 feedback: {reason}\nRevise and resubmit;
    stop
  endif
endif

'
' -------------------------------------
'  PHASE 6 . DEPLOY
' -------------------------------------
|Platform (Automated)|
#00695C:<color:#FFFFFF><b>  \u2465 DEPLOY  \u00b7  Schedule & Execute  </b></color>;

:Add rule to **ANOMALY_DETECTION_JOB**\n//priority P1/P2/P3 \u00b7 DEPLOY_ENV routing//;
note right #B2DFDB: <font color="#1B5E20"><b>STATUS = ACTIVE</b></font> (running on schedule)
:Execute on schedule / event trigger\nResults written \u2192 check_execution_log;

'
' -------------------------------------
'  PHASE 7 . MONITOR
' -------------------------------------
#B71C1C:<color:#FFFFFF><b>  \u2466 MONITOR  \u00b7  Detect \u00b7 Diagnose \u00b7 Alert  </b></color>;

:Detect anomalies **(D1)**\nDiagnose drift + blast radius **(D2)**;
:Violation detected:\n  Dispatch Email + Jira by priority\n  Log \u2192 DIGITAL_DATA_ANOMALIES;

|User|
:View rule health dashboard:\n  Pass rate \u00b7 Trend \u00b7 False-positive rate\n  DBU cost \u00b7 MTTD;

'
' -------------------------------------
'  PHASE 8 . IMPROVE
' -------------------------------------
#0277BD:<color:#FFFFFF><b>  \u2467 IMPROVE  \u00b7  Tune \u00b7 Optimise \u00b7 Evolve  </b></color>;

:Review noisy / low-value rules\nAdjust thresholds \u00b7 add exceptions\nPause or retire the rule;
note right #BBDEFB
  Status transitions:
  ACTIVE \u2192 INACTIVE / DISABLED
  INACTIVE \u2192 ACTIVE  (re-enable)
  ACTIVE \u2192 DEPRECATED \u2192 ARCHIVED
end note

|DQ Chatbot App|
:Surface tuning recommendations:\n//"Which rules are noisy or stale?"//;

|DQ Backend App|
:Apply tuning as version bump\n//version_id++ \u2192 re-enters VALIDATE//;
note right #C8E6C9
  Continuous Improvement Loop:
  MONITOR insights \u2192 IMPROVE
  IMPROVE re-enters VALIDATE
  Coverage + signal quality compound over time.
end note

stop

@enduml